column5: This is a charming 1930s duplex in Oak Cliff near Bishop's Arts District and Kessler. This is my home that I AirBNB when I visit my girlfriend in Austin.  This is a residential neighborhood and parking is in the driveway. Very close to coffee shops, bars and retail shops.   14 minute drive or $9 Lyft to downtown, Design District and the Dallas Art Museum. 18 minute drive or $11 Lyft to Deep Ellum.   Dogs are welcome. I have a backyard.
column8: Big Private One-Bedroom near Bishop Arts District
